### Get all locations (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/locations

### Get all locations (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/locations?page=2&limit=10

### Get location by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/locations/3

### Create location
POST http://localhost:5000/api/locations HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "New test location",
  "country": "United States of America"
}

### Update location
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/locations HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": 13,
  "title": "Updated location",
  "country": "United States of America"
}

### Delete location
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/locations/10 HTTP/1.1
